PrecisThe PREPARED BABY FOOD ANTI-DUMPING DUTY REMISSION ORDER provides for the reimbursement of some of the anti-dumping duties paid or payable under the Special Import Measures Act. This Remission Order is exempted from publication, inspection and copying pursuant to subsections 15(2) and 22(3) of the Statutory Instruments Regulations.
